net.usikkert.kouinject.generics
Class TypeMap

java.lang.Object
  net.usikkert.kouinject.generics.TypeMap

public class TypeMap
extends Object

A wrapper around a map with TypeVariable as key and Type as value. This is used when resolving actual type parameters of a class.

Author:
Christian Ihle
